      <talk_answer link_index="n016_trader_borin-accepting-d" mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>(……...) Let me see what items you have.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="9"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Borin$<BR>Oh, then welcome, valued customer! We always treat our customers with <FONT color=#a82424>respect</FONT> and <FONT color=#a82424>honesty</FONT>, as I'm sure you've noticed. That's how we've maintained our <FONT color=#dc5a00>number</FONT> <FONT color=#a82424>1</FONT> standing in the blacksmithing field for the past <FONT color=#dc5a00>10</FONT> <FONT color=#a82424>consecutive years</FONT>. We've always upheld our commitment to supplying <FONT color=#a82424>quality items</FONT> to you, our adoring patron, with the <FONT color=#a82424>dignity</FONT> you've come to expect.<BR>What can I do for you today?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n016_trader_borin-accepting-d" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300150">
      <talk_answer link_index="n016_trader_borin-accepting-e" mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>A relic box? What?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="13"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Borin$<BR>Since you are my special customer. Well, friend, I have something special for you! Let me show you a beautiful <FONT color=#a82424>Relic Box</FONT>, passed down from my ancestors, at a low, low price of <FONT color=#dc5a00>10</FONT><FONT color=#a82424>Gold</FONT>, and not a copper more!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
