      <talk_answer link_index="n016_trader_borin-1-a" mid="22"><![CDATA[<html>Sounds like…just any normal box.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="21"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Borin$<BR>A <FONT color=#a82424>Relic Box</FONT> is a box that <FONT color=#a82424>contains a special surprise</FONT> inside!<BR>No one knows what it contains until <FONT color=#a82424>it's being opened</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n016_trader_borin-1-a" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300150">
      <talk_answer link_index="n016_trader_borin-1-b" mid="24"><![CDATA[<html>I don’t think I have the money to afford it.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="23"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Borin$<BR>...<BR>But it's a <FONT color=#a82424>Relic Box</FONT>! It might contain something very valuable inside? I'm sure such a wise young adventurer like yourself cannot resist such a treasure temptations, hmm?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
