   <talk_paragraph index="n016_trader_borin-1-c" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300150">
      <talk_answer link_index="n016_trader_borin-1-d" mid="30"><![CDATA[<html>... Thanks?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="27"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Borin$<BR>Guess what? You may be just another freeloader who just sells nothing but junk and never purchase anything, thus making me poorer and poorer, but you since are a regular customer. I'll write an <FONT color=#a82424>IOU</FONT> for the box, just this time. Here, open up the <FONT color=#a82424>Relic Box</FONT> and see what's inside.</html>]]></talk_question>
