   <talk_paragraph index="n016_trader_borin-2-e" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300151">
      <talk_answer link_index="n016_trader_borin-2-f" mid="48"><![CDATA[<html>Wait a minute. You mean it cannot be used?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="47"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Borin$<BR>Heh...heheheheh. But, it doesn't matter. That is a weapon that <FONT color=#a82424>cannot be used</FONT> in today's world.<BR>It's only value is as an <FONT color=#a82424>antique</FONT>.<BR>It might be better to break it down and make an entirely new weapon from it.</html>]]></talk_question>
