      <talk_question mid="49"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Borin$<BR>You can try to use it but there won't be anything special.<BR>Only <FONT color=#dc5a00>Ancients</FONT> that wield this weapon can possess its power. The <FONT color=#dc5a00>Ancients</FONT> has been long gone, hundreds of years ago. The weapon is basically useless now.</html>]]></talk_question>
