   <talk_paragraph index="n016_trader_borin-2-g" image="QS_Default.dds" itemindex="300151">
      <talk_answer link_index="n016_trader_borin-2-h" mid="53"><![CDATA[<html>How can a weapon only be useful when wielded by Ancients? Why not us?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="51"><![CDATA[<html>$Blacksmith Borin$<BR>It hurts to say that such an <FONT color=#a82424>ancient relic</FONT> must be <FONT color=#a82424>dismantled</FONT>, but it's all a part of the circle of life.<BR>The useless are consumed and reformed to become useful. Destruction yields creation! Hahaha!</html>]]></talk_question>
